## **SECTION 12: FAQ**
```
❓ Frequently Asked Questions

Q: How long until my system is ready?
A: 7-10 days from when you approve the proposal. You'll be live 
   and selling within 2 weeks.

Q: What if my customers don't like talking to AI?
A: Our AI sounds natural and helpful. Plus, it can transfer to you 
   anytime for complex questions. Customers love the instant responses.

Q: Do I need technical knowledge?
A: Zero. We build everything, train the AI on your products, and 
   hand it to you ready to use. You just approve and go live.

Q: What if something breaks?
A: 90-day support included. We fix any issues fast. After 90 days, 
   support is available at ₦50,000/month or hourly rates.

Q: Are there any ongoing costs?
A: Yes, minimal monthly credits for the AI and messaging services. 
   These are usage-based, so you only pay for what you use - and it's 
   significantly less than hiring even one employee. We'll explain the 
   exact costs during your consultation based on your business volume.

Q: Can I see it working for my actual business first?
A: Yes! Book a free consultation and we'll show you a custom demo 
   with YOUR products in the system.

Q: What if I don't get results?
A: The AI works - it responds instantly and handles conversations 
   perfectly. But you need to drive traffic to your Instagram/WhatsApp. 
   We give you the system; you bring the customers.

Q: Why can't I see pricing on the website?
A: Because your system is custom-built for your business. We need to 
   understand your products, volume, and needs before we can give you 
   an accurate quote. Every business is different.

Q: Do you offer payment plans?
A: We discuss payment options during the consultation based on your 
   business size and needs.
